Rating: 4
So good! We loved this. My only change was to use a cup of veg stock in place of the water and a 1/2 tsp of sriracha (garlic chili sauce) in place of the chili flakes. The sauce was delicious and the broccoflower consistency is perfect. Next time I make this (and there will be a next time) I will add a bit more garlic. By the way, most might know this, but just in case (for those who don't): Broccoflower is the same thing as green cauliflower. It just depends on what brand your grocer carries. Try this, you'll love it.

