Rating: 3
I crossed this recipe with Broccoflower with Anchovies and garlic: I cooked the broccoflower in florets for about 10-15 minutes, drained it, then stir-fried it in olive oil with pine nuts and garlic, and balsamic vinegar. I then topped it with parmesan cheese (I forgot the basil). It was good.

